<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" type="text/css">
    <title>Event Request</title>
    <style>
        form {
            width: 60%;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background-color: #F9F9F9;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        input,
        button {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        input[type="checkbox"],
        input[type="radio"] {
            width: auto;
            margin-right: 5px;
        }
        button {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            font-size: 14px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        button:hover {
            background-color: #45A049;
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <div class="nav-container">
            <a href="/" class="project-name">Turtle Shelter Project</a>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/page2">Volunteer Application</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <h1>Event Request Form</h1>
    <form action="/host" method="POST">
        <!-- Main/Host Contact Info -->
        <p>Thank you for your interest in helping us save lives and accomplish our goal! 
            Fill our your information below and we will be in touch about the details. 
            Please be aware that we are nearly fully booked for about 6 months in advance,
            but we will do all that we can to accomodate you as soon as we can. 
            Please note that contact info should be for the primary point of contact for the event.
        </p>
        <label for="first_name">First Name:</label>
        <input type="text" id="first_name" name="first_name" required style="text-transform: uppercase;" oninput="this.value = this.value.toUpperCase()">
        <label for="last_name">Last Name:</label>
        <input type="text" id="last_name" name="last_name" required style="text-transform: uppercase;" oninput="this.value = this.value.toUpperCase()">
        <label for="phone">Phone Number:</label>
        <input type="text" id="phone" name="phone" required>
        <label for="host_email">Email:</label>
        <input type="text" id="host_email" name="host_email" required>
        <!-- Event Details -->
        <label for="organization">Organization:</label>
        <input type="text" id="organization" name="organization" required style="text-transform: uppercase;" oninput="this.value = this.value.toUpperCase()">
        <label for="description">Description of event (i.e. Company Holiday Service Event):</label>
        <input type="text" id="description" name="description" required>
        <!-- Event Location -->
        <label for="street">Street:</label>
        <input type="text" id="street" name="street" required style="text-transform: uppercase;" oninput="this.value = this.value.toUpperCase()">
        <label for="city">City:</label>
        <input type="text" id="city" name="city" required style="text-transform: uppercase;" oninput="this.value = this.value.toUpperCase()">
        <label for="state">State:</label>
        <input type="text" id="state" name="state" required style="text-transform: uppercase;" oninput="this.value = this.value.toUpperCase()">
        <label for="zip">Zip:</label>
        <input type="text" id="zip" name="zip" required>
        <p>Please list your top 2 date preferences. If neither will work for our current schedule,
             we will continue searching together for a date that would work together.</p>
        <!-- Possible Event Dates -->
        <label for="possible_date_1">Top Date Preference:</label>
        <input type="datetime-local" id="possible_date_1" name="possible_date_1" required>
        <label for="possible_date_2">Second Date Preference:</label>
        <input type="datetime-local" id="possible_date_2" name="possible_date_2" required>
        <!-- Event Length -->
        <label for="event_length">Event Length (Hours):</label>
        <input type="number" step="0.5" id="event_length" name="event_length" required>
        <!-- Activity Type -->
        <p>Some events involve sewing tasks while others involve other steps of fabrication, 
            including pinning and cutting fabric, including other simpler activities more suitable for children under 10.
             Which type of activities would you like your event to include?</p>
        <label>Select Type of Activity:</label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="sewing_abbreviation" value="S" checked> Sewing</label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="sewing_abbreviation" value="N"> Non-Sewing</label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="sewing_abbreviation" value="B"> Both</label>
        <!-- Types of Participants -->
        <p>Non-sewing roles will not require exact numbers for materials and equiptment, but we need exact counts for 
            children under 10 and sewers attending the event in order to prepare the correct amount of materials. Please note that 
            for our counts to be correct, those bringing sewing machines are expected to participate in the sewing activities on their own machine.</p>
        <label for="number_of_sewers">Number of Sewers:</label>
        <input type="number" step="1" id="number_of_sewers" name="number_of_sewers" required>
        <label for="number_of_nonsewers">Number of Non-Sewers:</label>
        <input type="number" step="1" id="number_of_nonsewers" name="number_of_nonsewers" required>
        <label for="number_of_children">Number of Children (Younger than 10):</label>
        <input type="number" step="1" id="number_of_children" name="number_of_children" required>
        <!-- Sewing Machines -->
        <label for="machine">Number of People Bringing Sewing Machines:</label>
        <input type="number" step="1" id="machine" name="machine" required>
        <!-- Jen's Story -->
        <p>Many events begin with a presentation from Jen about her story that inspired the founding of the Turtle Shelter Project. </p>
        <label>
            <input type="checkbox" id="jen_story" name="jen_story" value="true">
            Would you like to hear Jen's Story at your event?
        </label>
        <!-- Submit Button -->
        <button type="submit">Submit Application</button>
    </form>
</body>
</html>
